name: The Dragon Warrior - Psy Energy - Render Version
description: Marcelo Alt, 2019. This piece was originally created as a scenography for the Psy Energy music festival in Goiânia, Brazil. The idea is a Warrior Mage who invokes his spells to manipulate the minds of the audience. This spell was called "The Dragon Resurrection." The magic words are: "When the dragon's power is released." | @vj_alt | www.artstation.com/vjalt |
